既左翼理論研究經濟姐。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"呢個我諗要熟哂兩邊嘅人先會有好嘅insight<br />\n你知stem同humanities唔少人人係兩邊互屌但其實對對方嘅field係零認識<br />\n我覺得有時d媒體鬧經濟學會誇張左<br />\n可能因為佢地嘅理論太影響到人 <br />\n容易賺view<br />\n對經濟嘅critique都有好多種<br />\n有d係覺得model無factor到好多野所以唔完整<br />\n所以以前上個世紀嘅理論黎address我地社會問題係會出事<br />\n(例如窮人嘅vicious cycle/窮人攞welfare會唔會唔做野/inequality太大會唔會更低效/邊d方面要大政府 好似研究話eds and meds pay for itself etc)<br />\n都可以叫同左翼有關嘅<br />\n雖然好少economist係嗰種話要abolish private ownership嗰種<br />\n佢地嘅critique都係由自己field出發<br />\n唔會同你平時睇嘅差好遠<br />\nHeterodox嗰類可能係你想睇嗰類<br />\n不過我唔識<br />\n同埋可以睇political economy/philosophy呢d<br />\n始終傾社會問題時唔會淨係講有無效率呢d<br />\n都會講有無moral basis呢d(private ownership(and of what?land?labour effort?)/debt/public good)<br />\n或者economic anthropology/economic sociology/economic history<br />\n可以有多d insight去睇我地嘅社會體系/關係係depends on/born out of what"},{"pid":"205042e7da2ef5e81619e964fcfe00bfdf61a069","tid":2205280,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d6c3c1f5fe90aa54c6192d500ac3c75631ae09","tid":2205280,"uid":86662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c1af547c1e8c58bbb5613f92630cfdfb711bb3","tid":2205280,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a982e28fa67520be936bb55d0c2199d49d8d524d","tid":2205280,"uid":86662,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"吹到D左翼理論，讀過下書，政黨都計啦。開放討論。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"咪你嗰堆<br />\n仲有夜貓<br />\nBtw佢地路線都有唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:29:30.000Z","msg":"咁國際左翼media 有邊D<br />\n英國有In Defence of Marxism <br />\n美國有JACOBIN <br />\n仲有無D係高質？中國又有無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"Search下leftist/socialist magazine/journal"},{"pid":"841f699dfd51e554daedb2e0ccb229d16249e26f","tid":2205280,"uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29860792328905c9c1034bab0875e942ec5bd70d","tid":2205280,"uid":86662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a0bc62